(define/contract (length-of-longest-subsequence nums target)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  (let loop ((nums nums) (target target) (max-len -1) (current-len 0) (current-sum 0))
    (cond
     ((null? nums)
      max-len)
     ((= current-sum target)
      (loop (cdr nums) target (max max-len current-len) 0 0))
     ((> current-sum target)
      (loop (cdr nums) target max-len (if (> current-len 0) (- current-len 1) 0) (if (> current-len 0) (- current-sum (car nums)) 0)))
     (else
      (let ((include (loop (cdr nums) target max-len (+ current-len 1) (+ current-sum (car nums))))
            (exclude (loop (cdr nums) target max-len current-len current-sum)))
        (max include exclude)))))
  )
